View selection for call from OSP001B 1= All 2 = Errors only
M: Modify invoice OSP001C, reinitialize when returning
N: OSP001C in create mode, reinitialize when returning
Call only if schedule is not being processed by another user
Q: Query Invoice
Display Info
I: Initialize
O: Online
... for country NL the resolution must be 1024x768, because of extended view
... for the remaining countries still 800x600 has to be used
C: Cancel
D: Delete, mark selected invoice as "deleted", update totals
exit and reinitialize
N: New, call OSP001C in createmode
S:Select, modify/query Invoice using OSP001C
If modify is disabled call in query mode
Else in modify mode
T:Totals open totals screen and return Online
